{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:0","text":"允许 GPrim primitive variables（primvars）通过 pattern graphs 传递。"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:1","text":"Input Parameters"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:2","text":"Variable"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:3","text":"定义 variable 的样式"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:4","text":"Variable Name"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:5","text":"primitive variable 的名称。"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:6","text":"Variable Type"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:7","text":"primitive variable 的类型："}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:8","text":"float"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:9","text":"float2"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:10","text":"color"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:11","text":"point"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:12","text":"vector"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:13","text":"normal"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:14","text":"Default Float"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:15","text":"如果检索类型为 'float' 的 variable 时出错，将使用此值。"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:16","text":"Verbosity"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:17","text":"用于 scene debugging（场景调试）的 diagnostic output levels（诊断输出级别）"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:18","text":"Output Parameters"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:19","text":"result"}
{"item_id":"e95e86e75d:20","text":"以 color 形式输出的 result。"}
